commit.message:
darwin-weakimport-1.c: Use -fno-asynchronous-unwind-tables.

2006-10-13  Eric Christopher  <echristo@apple.com>

        * gcc.dg/darwin-weakimport-1.c: Use
        -fno-asynchronous-unwind-tables.
        * gcc.dg/darwin-weakimport-3.c: Ditto.

From-SVN: r117711
